<i>♪ I never died says he ♪</i>

49:23.025 --> 49:29.863
<i>♪ I never died says he ♪</i>

49:29.968 --> 49:36.039
<i>♪ Says he ♪</i>

49:45.483 --> 49:49.318
Hey. Are you all right?

49:49.927 --> 49:51.268
Oh.

49:51.853 --> 49:53.002
Oh, oh, oh!

49:53.013 --> 49:54.448
Look at her.

49:54.459 --> 49:57.227
She's a work of art.

49:57.511 --> 50:01.012
And we made her. Together.

50:02.312 --> 50:06.252
Paloma.
We will call her Paloma.

50:07.973 --> 50:09.506
Paloma.

50:09.517 --> 50:10.517
Yes.

50:10.528 --> 50:12.387
Now that's a lovely name.

50:12.398 --> 50:15.799
That way we can be sure.

50:15.827 --> 50:17.560
Sure of what?

50:17.571 --> 50:21.574
That we will always
have peace in our family.

